            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Verterio <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Luco <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Secundo <lb n="5"/>militi <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VIII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>|(centuriae) <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>exti</ex></expan> Octavi Primani <lb n="7"/>stipendiorum II <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>frat</abbr><ex>ri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pient</abbr><ex>issimo</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>rater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Stele mit dreieckigem Abschluss, oben abgebrochen. Bruch leicht schräg durch den oberen Teil auf Höhe von Z. 2. Im Giebelfeld Akanthusornament mit Rosette. Zahlreiche Ligaturen: Z. 5: MI, LI, AV; Z. 6: CT, AV, RI, NI; Z. 7: TI, PE, DI; Z. 8: RI. Z. 9: auch f(aciendum) d(e) s(uo)... möglich.</p>
            </div>
